export const keyStoreSchema = {
	type: 'object',
	required: ['crypto', 'id', 'version', 'address'],
	properties: {
		crypto: {
			type: 'object',
			required: ['cipher', 'ciphertext', 'cipherparams', 'kdf', 'kdfparams', 'mac'],
			properties: {
				cipher: { type: 'string' },
				ciphertext: { type: 'string' },
				cipherparams: { type: 'object' },
				kdf: { type: 'string' },
				kdfparams: { type: 'object' },
				salt: { type: 'string' },
				mac: { type: 'string' },
			},
		},
		id: { type: 'string' },
		version: { type: 'number' },
		address: { type: 'string' },
	},
};
